Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.23,0:00:03.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Love and hate are brought together...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.06,0:00:04.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Through both reasoning and suspense!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.98,0:00:06.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can a case like this really happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.77,0:00:08.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Crimes cannot be recycled
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.61,0:00:10.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seeing through to the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.36,0:00:12.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I look like a child, but have the intellect of an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.16,0:00:14.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My name is Detective Conan
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.75,0:01:50.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That day, I went to Akebono with the rest of the Detective Boys to apprehend a thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.42,0:01:54.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll definitely catch him together! Won't we, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.01,0:02:00.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doesn't it make you feel a little uneasy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.89,0:02:03.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Other people reuse materials that can still be put to use.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.27,0:02:09.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's an amazing system, in which we are able to help preserve our limited resources.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.90,0:02:12.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh! You're talking about recycling.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.94,0:02:17.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you don't know what kind of person used it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.70,0:02:18.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, Conan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.95,0:02:20.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.12,0:02:24.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There aren't many people that wipe their boogers on everything, unlike Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} here...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.70,0:02:27.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh my gosh, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!\NIs that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.00,0:02:28.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.88,0:02:30.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't say things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.75,0:02:33.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop it. I'm just stating what I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.88,0:02:36.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! It's the bus to Akebono!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.84,0:02:38.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, it really is!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.97,0:02:44.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Victim Who Came Back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.53,0:02:58.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's too quiet. There's no one around.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.82,0:03:01.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe that's because there's a thief around.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.78,0:03:04.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, watch out for anyone suspicious-looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.75,0:03:09.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What am I doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.88,0:03:14.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It came from that room!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.34,0:03:17.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Wait up, Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.80,0:03:21.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.35,0:03:25.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.39,0:03:28.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this okay, Conan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.24,0:03:41.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.20,0:03:51.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was struck on the back of the head and died from a brain injury.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.62,0:03:56.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We estimate the time of death to be around 2 to 3 PM yesterday afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.59,0:04:01.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, she was not carrying any form of identification.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.51,0:04:07.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hosono{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, please give us a description of the body when you found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.89,0:04:09.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.35,0:04:10.52,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I bought that sofa yesterday evening at the recycle shop in Beika.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.19,0:04:20.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it was delivered this morning at 10 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.57,0:04:27.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I noticed the seat cushions were lopsided, but when I tried to fix them...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.13,0:04:39.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The old lady was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.76,0:04:40.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.42,0:04:44.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you know the victim?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.22,0:04:46.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I did not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.05,0:04:49.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, where were you yesterday from 2:00 to 3:00 PM?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.39,0:04:52.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A-Are you suspecting me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.98,0:04:57.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, not at all. I just have to take every last thing into consideration.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.07,0:05:00.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was at the movies all afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.40,0:05:02.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Were you with anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.57,0:05:03.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I went alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.36,0:05:08.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you think Inspector Megure suspects her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.03,0:05:09.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.25,0:05:14.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can think of only two possibilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.83,0:05:17.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Either Hosono Sanae{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} killed the victim...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.54,0:05:22.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And made it look as though the body was in the sofa when it was delivered...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.63,0:05:27.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or, the body really was already inside the sofa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.64,0:05:32.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, when we arrived, she had such a shocked and scared look on her face!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.48,0:05:36.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It didn't look like she was pretending at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.90,0:05:38.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.40,0:05:38.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.48,0:05:43.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's our job as police to consider all possibilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.61,0:05:45.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.58,0:05:51.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, Inspector...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.37,0:05:57.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder why the old lady inside the sofa didn't have her shoes on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.25,0:06:02.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It means she might not have been wearing them when she was murdered.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.38,0:06:07.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see! So that means she was murdered inside a room and moved later, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.97,0:06:11.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If she is the culprit, then the murder had to have taken place here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.64,0:06:13.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, please go question the neighbors.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.98,0:06:14.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.06,0:06:21.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.61,0:06:25.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.95,0:06:27.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The apartment next door?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.86,0:06:29.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me. What is your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.87,0:06:34.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-It's Tokunaga... Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.37,0:06:40.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually... Your neighbor, Hosono{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, found a dead body inside her sofa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.79,0:06:47.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tokunaga{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, were you in your room yesterday between 2 and 3 PM?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.68,0:06:49.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.64,0:06:51.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I work in the evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.56,0:06:58.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you notice any strange noises, voices, or anything out of the ordinary next door?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.10,0:07:02.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please think carefully and try to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.44,0:07:07.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it, I think I heard someone arguing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.28,0:07:10.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you did hear something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.82,0:07:12.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.24,0:07:15.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.87,0:07:19.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure... I couldn't hear it very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.17,0:07:23.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that right? Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.34,0:07:26.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll come back later if I need anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.42,0:07:27.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.72,0:07:36.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder if what he just said is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.06,0:07:40.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's kind of hard to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.31,0:07:45.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In this case, she may have been lying about going to the movies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.78,0:07:47.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.53,0:07:48.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.95,0:07:53.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd like to look into that recycle shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.58,0:07:56.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't stop thinking about what the children said.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.58,0:07:58.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Officer Takagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.41,0:08:01.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.29,0:08:02.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure. Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.17,0:08:04.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.63,0:08:11.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you're inquiring about that sofa, we received it as a donation from a customer yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.97,0:08:16.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yesterday? And you immediately put it up for display?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.10,0:08:21.35,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Yes. Hosono{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} came right when the sofa was being brought here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.35,0:08:26.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told her that it would take a few days to mend, but she told me she was in a hurry and couldn't wait that long.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.28,0:08:29.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And what about after she bought it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.36,0:08:33.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was in the store until closing time...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.07,0:08:37.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After which, we loaded it into the delivery truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.37,0:08:40.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could anyone else have gotten near the truck?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.29,0:08:43.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.08,0:08:45.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The truck was parked in the garage...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.75,0:08:49.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And we locked it right after the sofa was loaded on it, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.09,0:08:50.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.30,0:08:53.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.18,0:08:58.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The old lady was already in the sofa when it was bought.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.77,0:09:02.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the culprit was the previous owner of the sofa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.69,0:09:14.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To be honest, I didn't receive that sofa as a donation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.28,0:09:16.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Hirose{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.95,0:09:21.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't you say that a customer came and gave it to you for free?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.16,0:09:23.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.87,0:09:27.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yesterday afternoon, I drove around to pick up unwanted items.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.38,0:09:30.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was around 4:00 PM, and I was on my way home...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.97,0:09:40.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Hirose{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.02,0:09:45.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that a waste? It looks like it could still be used.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.44,0:09:49.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.36,0:09:54.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You picked it up at a dump?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.07,0:09:54.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.49,0:10:01.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because it looked like it was still in good condition, and I felt sorry for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.49,0:10:02.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.66,0:10:04.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.87,0:10:09.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I understand your feelings about not wanting to let it go to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.17,0:10:13.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, now that we know it was picked up at a dump...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.63,0:10:17.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no way we'll find the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.01,0:10:17.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.68,0:10:20.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, Officer Takagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.31,0:10:25.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it hard to believe that the culprit would move it there from very far away?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.44,0:10:28.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.06,0:10:31.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which garbage dump did you find the sofa in?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.73,0:10:33.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it was in...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.65,0:10:35.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...Akebono, on 3rd Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.95,0:10:38.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akebono?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.88,0:10:56.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're back to where we started.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.76,0:10:59.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that old lady...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.55,0:11:00.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.47,0:11:03.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was left here yesterday at 4:00 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.10,0:11:06.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then was picked up and taken to the recycle shop...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.73,0:11:10.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, finally, was returned here via the delivery truck at 10:00 AM.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.11,0:11:15.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit most likely lives in this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.07,0:11:16.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, how are we going to find him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.11,0:11:22.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, why would someone put the body in an old sofa?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.45,0:11:24.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.41,0:11:30.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah! They didn't think anyone would bother an old sofa in a garbage dump.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.08,0:11:30.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.04,0:11:33.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're starting to do that "but" thing again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.92,0:11:37.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have a bad habit of denying the truth, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.47,0:11:40.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look who's talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.22,0:11:43.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Some people just creep me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.35,0:11:50.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This morning, Tokunaga{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was alone at that restaurant drinking beer and laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.98,0:11:53.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh? That guy actually laughs?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.98,0:11:56.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He always seems so serious when I see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.32,0:11:59.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I think something big must have happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.49,0:12:04.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tokunaga?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.58,0:12:06.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that the man we saw this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.29,0:12:08.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hosono Sanae{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s neighbor?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.37,0:12:11.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.54,0:12:13.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh! Inspector Megure!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.13,0:12:16.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.75,0:12:20.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hosono{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s alibi was able to be confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.18,0:12:25.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone at the movie theater remembered seeing her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.47,0:12:27.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.22,0:12:29.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if that's the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.39,0:12:34.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tokunaga{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} most likely mistook something else as those voices.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.02,0:12:36.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A mistake?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.69,0:12:43.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, while we were trying to find where the sofa came from, we ended up back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.87,0:12:49.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The victim was definitely put in the sofa here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.46,0:12:52.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll search for some witnesses!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.92,0:12:54.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm leaving it to you, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.84,0:12:59.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know who the culprit is!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.84,0:13:02.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really, Mitsuhiko?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.01,0:13:04.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.18,0:13:07.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tokunaga{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} didn't mishear the argument.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.43,0:13:10.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Most likely, there never was one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.48,0:13:12.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Inspector Megure said...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.73,0:13:17.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it obvious?\NThe culprit is Tokunaga{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.07,0:13:20.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's the culprit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.29,0:13:36.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those women were right, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.50,0:13:40.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She said that Tokunaga guy was in a really good mood this morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.63,0:13:42.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now we know the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.80,0:13:46.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tokunaga{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is definitely the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.05,0:13:51.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, for what purpose do murderers hide their victim's bodies?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.23,0:13:54.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the body won't be discovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.31,0:13:58.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it was discovered, it would be identified.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.44,0:14:04.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The police would investigate around the area and eventually find the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.70,0:14:07.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why you would hide it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.20,0:14:09.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.16,0:14:16.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, you would have a better chance if you hid the body in the mountains or in the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.08,0:14:18.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why didn't the culprit do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.13,0:14:22.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I don't get that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.51,0:14:23.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,True...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.88,0:14:26.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's only one solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.76,0:14:31.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tokunaga{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} actually wanted to go to the mountains or the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.22,0:14:34.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, it was impossible for him to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.02,0:14:36.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why was it impossible?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.40,0:14:39.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Remember what he said?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.19,0:14:45.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He works during the evenings.\NThat's why he wouldn't be able to go far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.53,0:14:54.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see. Adults can't skip out on work. Right, Officer Takagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.58,0:14:55.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.79,0:15:00.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tokunaga{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} placed the body in the sofa, only intending to hide it there temporarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.34,0:15:03.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Temporarily?"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.00,0:15:04.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.17,0:15:08.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After work, he was planning to hide it properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.97,0:15:13.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But after work, when he came back to get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.93,0:15:18.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The recycle shop's delivery truck had already picked it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.48,0:15:20.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.07,0:15:26.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When he returned from work, Tokunaga{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was probably shocked to find that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.90,0:15:30.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The sofa had disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.66,0:15:34.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, his shock turned into utter joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.87,0:15:38.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, someone took the body away for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.50,0:15:46.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since he didn't have to get rid of the body, he was able to celebrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.22,0:15:53.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, upon returning home, he found that the unthinkable had occurred.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.01,0:15:59.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The body that he thought had disappeared was found next door.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.48,0:16:07.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, the police's primary suspect was Hosono Sanae{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, who discovered the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.69,0:16:10.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tokunaga{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} took advantage of this and decided to lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.03,0:16:15.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it, I think I heard someone arguing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.25,0:16:19.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That wasn't a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.91,0:16:23.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He lied to try and frame Hosono{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} as the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.84,0:16:27.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everything makes sense now, Mitsuhiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.05,0:16:27.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.34,0:16:31.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it was nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.18,0:16:33.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.76,0:16:41.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if he had to go to work, why would the culprit need to move the body?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.77,0:16:42.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.81,0:16:47.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He could have just left it in his room, locked the door, and no one would've been the wiser.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.23,0:16:50.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see. I guess that's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.24,0:16:55.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did we come to Akebono to do today?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.83,0:17:00.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To look for the thief who's been robbing homes around this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.41,0:17:04.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tokunaga{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was afraid the thief would break in!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.08,0:17:12.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh! If the thief saw the victim, he'd report it to the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.68,0:17:15.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.05,0:17:18.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's why he couldn't leave the body in his room!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.31,0:17:21.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's a perfect deduction, Mitsuhiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.48,0:17:25.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. That's impossible, Mitsuhiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.03,0:17:32.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Listen. Think carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.24,0:17:41.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you think the chances of someone seeing him hide the body are greater than the thief breaking in?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.46,0:17:49.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And would he really be happy to see his sofa gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.84,0:17:54.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't a person normally be worried that the police might have found it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.97,0:18:01.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, he could have simply called in sick for a day, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.72,0:18:06.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, you simply assumed Tokunaga{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.15,0:18:11.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cases aren't that simple. Let's thin this through again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.99,0:18:14.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}! I'll say this now, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.24,0:18:18.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who is the one assuming things?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.78,0:18:24.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you keep saying "normally," but a lot of people are really wary of the recent robberies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.21,0:18:28.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He probably felt lucky to find the body gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.04,0:18:33.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And someone who never misses work would fear they'd look suspicious if they missed even a single day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.38,0:18:38.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't there weak-hearted people who go to work every day just because they can't speak up for themselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.98,0:18:54.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,According to the janitor, Tokunaga{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} owns a small bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.03,0:19:00.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Despite the financial difficulties, he works everyday.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.45,0:19:02.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's a serious, timid person...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.54,0:19:04.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or at least that's what the janitor said.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.08,0:19:08.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just as Mitsuhiko predicted.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.92,0:19:13.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He has to get the store ready, so he leaves at this time everyday.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.59,0:19:16.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,3:00 PM, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.05,0:19:17.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.30,0:19:23.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He wouldn't know for sure if the thief would break in. Would he really be that wary?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.31,0:19:28.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Attention citizens!\NThere have been a number of burglaries in this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.60,0:19:32.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please be sure to lock up your house before you leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.32,0:19:35.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Once again, this is the Akebono Police.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.40,0:19:35.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.74,0:19:36.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.49,0:19:38.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.91,0:19:41.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Officer Takagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.82,0:19:44.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you drive around this area yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.24,0:19:47.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. If I remember correctly, we were here ten minutes earlier yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.12,0:19:50.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Officer Takagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.67,0:19:53.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's what happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.34,0:20:01.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After Tokunaga{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} murdered her, he heard them...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.59,0:20:04.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The voices from the patrol car!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.35,0:20:07.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the Akebono Police.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.56,0:20:12.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There have been a number of burglaries in this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.57,0:20:20.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After hearing this, you put her body inside a sofa and carried it to a dump.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.07,0:20:23.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Tokunaga{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.75,0:20:33.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Owed that lady money.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.29,0:20:41.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A-And when I asked her for an extra week to repay it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.59,0:20:49.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She barged into my apartment and told me that if I didn't pay her back in time, she would revoke my bar license.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.60,0:20:50.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.69,0:20:54.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I lost my senses.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.48,0:21:00.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.82,0:21:05.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tokunaga{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, please follow me to the police station.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.37,0:21:06.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.20,0:21:09.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good job, Mitsuhiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.41,0:21:10.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.00,0:21:13.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mitsuhiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.67,0:21:17.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You deserve some kudos for your great deductions this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.48,0:22:59.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?! The thief in Akebono was caught a long time ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.69,0:23:06.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. A man who was arrested for theft last week just confessed to the other burglaries as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.53,0:23:11.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's with that?! We wanted to be the ones to catch him!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.41,0:23:14.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wasted all of that money on the bus fare, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.70,0:23:22.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, could it be that Tokunaga{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} didn't even need to bother with hiding the body in the sofa?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.92,0:23:28.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true, but our culprit didn't think things though, and slipped up because of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.72,0:23:31.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a hopeless criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.97,0:23:34.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.65,0:23:42.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey. You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.86,0:23:49.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mail she can't erase?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.24,0:23:53.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Has it already been three years since then?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.62,0:23:55.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They've heard it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.54,0:23:57.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The whispers of the demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.54,0:23:58.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Matsuda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.37,0:23:59.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't, Sato!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.67,0:24:01.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't! You'll set off the bomb's mercury lever!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.93,0:24:10.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.01,0:24:13.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next 2 Hour Special:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.93,0:24:16.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A Shaking Police HQ and 12 Million Hostages.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.77,0:24:20.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.35,0:24:21.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Map symbols.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.98,0:24:26.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please look forward to the next episode!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.40,0:24:23.90,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Next time will be a two-hour New Year's special!
